# Lumiu Implementation Plan

Lumiu is a sensory-safe, AI-powered learning platform designed for neurodivergent learners. This plan outlines the development phases, technical architecture, and design principles.

## 🌟 Vision & Goals
- **Inclusivity:** Accessible design for ADHD, dyslexia, and autism.
- **Sensory-Safe:** Muted colors, minimal animations, no guilt-based pressure.
- **Growth-Oriented:** Galaxy-themed progress visualization.
- **Offline-First:** PWA with local synchronization.

## 🛠️ Technical Stack
- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router), React, Vanilla CSS / CSS Modules.
- **Backend:** Node.js, PostgreSQL (via Prisma or similar).
- **AI:** Modular AI service for quiz generation.
- **Offline:** Service Workers, LocalStorage/IndexedDB.
- **Fonts:** Dyslexia-friendly typography (e.g., OpenDyslexic fallback, sans-serifs).

## 🗺️ Roadmap

### Phase 1: Foundation & Design System (Completed)
- [x] Initialize Next.js project.
- [x] Establish CSS Variables for muted blues/greens.
- [x] Setup core layouts (Calm Navigation).
- [x] Implement Galaxy Background (Stars as tasks).

### Phase 2: Core Learning Features (Completed)
- [x] Subject-based Decks & Flashcards/Notes (UI).
- [x] Spaced Repetition Visuals.
- [x] Focus Mode with Timer and Distraction-free toggle.
- [x] Galaxy Universe Dashboard.

### Phase 3: AI & PWA Integration
- [ ] AI Quiz generator (MCQ, T/F, Fill-in-blanks).
- [ ] Manifest and Service Worker setup.
- [ ] Offline data sync.

### Phase 4: Polish & Accessibility
- [ ] Dyslexia-friendly font toggles.
- [ ] Adjustable text size/spacing controls.
- [ ] 2D Fallback mode for performance.

## 🎨 Design System
### Colors
- **Backgrounds:** Deep midnight blue (calm, not black).
- **Accents:** Muted turquoise (#72a0a8), Soft Sage (#b8c9b9), Lavender Grey (#a6a6c4).
- **Text:** High contrast but soft (Off-white/Light Grey).

### Typography
- Primary: Inter or Outfit.
- Accessible: OpenDyslexic.

## 🚀 Execution Strategy
- Start with the **Galaxy Home Screen** to set the aesthetic tone.
- Implement **Deck/Flashcard** system with local storage first for immediate PWA feel.
- Integrate **AI** as a background service.
